headline.main: Fed Vice Chair Joins Effort to Flag Pending Rate Hike
headline.print_headline: Fed Vice Chair Joins Effort to Flag Pending Rate Hike

lead_paragraph: Austrian opposition parties setting up a parliamentary inquiry into the state's order for Eurofighter Typhoon jets 14 years ago have said they will seek to determine whether any kickbacks were paid to win the contract and to identify any officials who might have profited.
